===Etymology 2===
{{zh-forms|s=拨|alt=畀,不}}
Likely a glottalized variant of {{ltc-l|把|to hold; to give (dialectal)}} ({{zh-ref|Dai, 2004}}).

First attested as {{zh-l|撥垃|tr=peq-laq}} in ''Shan'ge'' ({{lang|zh|山歌}}) by {{w|zh:馮夢龍|Feng Menglong}}. It is, however, likely that the term was already common before this attestation.

